2
00:00:06,191 --> 00:00:08,601
Is this where Daeguk's CEO lives?

3
00:00:09,701 --> 00:00:11,870
- Who are you? - Who am I?

4
00:00:11,870 --> 00:00:13,970
I'm Oh Jeong Hoon's future mother-in-law.

5
00:00:13,970 --> 00:00:16,470
My niece is going to marry him.

6
00:00:17,740 --> 00:00:18,841
What?

7
00:00:18,841 --> 00:00:19,841
Why look so shocked?

8
00:00:19,841 --> 00:00:22,341
You didn't know he was engaged?

9
00:00:25,551 --> 00:00:28,181
Get out. Get out of my house.

10
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,880
Don't you yell at me.

11
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:31,790
Your daughter stole a man.

12
00:00:31,790 --> 00:00:34,121
What? She stole?

13
00:00:34,121 --> 00:00:36,291
Yes. They were engaged...

14
00:00:36,291 --> 00:00:38,860
and you stole him away with money.

15
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:41,901
What? With money?

16
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,301
My niece dated and supported Jeong Hoon...

17
00:00:44,301 --> 00:00:47,541
for four years while he studied for the bar.

18
00:00:47,541 --> 00:00:50,041
Now that he passed the bar,

19
00:00:50,041 --> 00:00:52,670
you waved money before him to pinch him.

20
00:00:52,670 --> 00:00:54,880
Do you think I'll let you do that?

21
00:00:56,081 --> 00:00:57,911
My goodness, no!

22
00:00:57,911 --> 00:00:59,280
What are you doing?

23
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,820
Get out. Get out!

24
00:01:02,051 --> 00:01:05,020
If you don't get out right now, I'll call the police!

25
00:01:05,020 --> 00:01:06,750
What? The police?

26
00:01:06,750 --> 00:01:08,690
Do you think that scares me?

27
00:01:08,690 --> 00:01:10,360
Call them. Call the police.

28
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:13,591
I will turn this thieving household upside-down.

29
00:01:13,731 --> 00:01:16,030
What? "Thieving"?

30
00:01:16,261 --> 00:01:18,371
Who are you calling a thief?

31
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:24,810
Hey, I've been through more than you think.

32
00:01:24,810 --> 00:01:28,181
Do you think I won't be able to deal with the likes of you?

33
00:01:28,181 --> 00:01:30,651
- Let go! - How dare you?

34
00:01:30,651 --> 00:01:31,810
- Let go! - Who are you?

35
00:01:31,810 --> 00:01:34,220
What do you think you are?

36
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:40,321
That woman is all brawn and no brains.

37
00:01:40,321 --> 00:01:42,761
She's no CEO's wife. She's a thug.

38
00:01:43,761 --> 00:01:45,330
I'll leave for now,

39
00:01:45,330 --> 00:01:48,030
but do you think I'll let you steal Jeong Hoon?

40
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:49,330
As if!

41
00:01:49,761 --> 00:01:50,871
My goodness.

42
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:04,250
What's all this? What's this mess?

43
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:05,780
Mom, what happened?

44
00:02:05,951 --> 00:02:09,120
Do you know what just happened because of you?

45
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:11,150
What happened?

46
00:02:11,291 --> 00:02:12,951
Why is this room a mess?

47
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:17,860
Jeong Hoon promised to marry someone else.

48
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:20,661
Her aunt just came and did this.

49
00:02:23,031 --> 00:02:25,101
You didn't know about that, did you?

50
00:02:25,370 --> 00:02:28,441
He conned all of us.

51
00:02:28,441 --> 00:02:30,441
He didn't con us.

52
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:32,770
He ended it with her.

53
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:33,881
What?

54
00:02:34,580 --> 00:02:37,911
Then you knew he had been dating someone else?

55
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:40,580
How could you still think of marrying him?

56
00:02:40,751 --> 00:02:42,650
She supported him for years!

57
00:02:45,691 --> 00:02:46,821
Where are you going?

58
00:02:48,821 --> 00:02:51,661
This is just unbelievable.

59
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:54,800
I was worried about you and...

60
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,960
wanted to see you.

61
00:02:57,531 --> 00:03:00,601
I didn't know you worked with my aunt.

62
00:03:01,471 --> 00:03:03,201
She isn't at work?

63
00:03:03,201 --> 00:03:04,571
If she left home,

64
00:03:04,571 --> 00:03:06,071
she'll show up later.

65
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,911
It's hard, isn't it?

66
00:03:13,251 --> 00:03:16,120
I can tell just by looking at your face.

67
00:03:17,751 --> 00:03:20,221
Do you know why Jeong Hoon...

68
00:03:20,221 --> 00:03:21,490
suddenly changed?

69
00:03:22,221 --> 00:03:24,390
What did he tell you?

70
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:25,761
He's seeing someone.

71
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:29,031
That won't be true.

72
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:32,571
I think he lied to make me give up.

73
00:03:35,001 --> 00:03:37,210
There has to be another reason.

74
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,340
Don't you know what it is?

75
00:03:40,610 --> 00:03:42,281
Not really.

76
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,210
Can you talk to your brother?

77
00:03:45,610 --> 00:03:49,221
I really don't know why he's acting like this.

78
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,321
Sure, I will.

79
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:54,420
Go back inside.

80
00:03:54,791 --> 00:03:55,990
You should rest.

81
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:57,631
Okay.

82
00:03:58,330 --> 00:03:59,330
Bye.

83
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,610
Floor manager?

84
00:04:11,571 --> 00:04:13,071
You're looking for me?

85
00:04:13,981 --> 00:04:15,710
You hadn't come to work,

86
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:17,111
so Mr. Jo sent me.

87
00:04:17,381 --> 00:04:18,850
I can't work today.

88
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:21,780
Tell the boss that I'm ill in bed.

89
00:04:22,321 --> 00:04:23,350
Then...

90
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:26,421
- let's have a chat. - About what?

91
00:04:29,821 --> 00:04:31,431
What did you just say?

92
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:34,261
You're Jeong Hoon's brother?

93
00:04:34,431 --> 00:04:36,660
I met Soon Young at your home...

94
00:04:36,861 --> 00:04:38,730
and just found out you're her aunt.

95
00:04:38,970 --> 00:04:40,671
This is a mess.

96
00:04:44,241 --> 00:04:47,011
You're Jeong Hoon's brother, so let me ask you something.

97
00:04:47,181 --> 00:04:48,840
When did he...

98
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,850
get together with Daeguk's CEO's daughter?

99
00:04:50,910 --> 00:04:52,710
Are they discussing marriage?

100
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:55,621
Don't think of lying.

101
00:04:55,621 --> 00:04:57,350
Mal Soon the seamstress knows.

102
00:04:57,350 --> 00:04:59,720
That means she visited the family.

103
00:04:59,850 --> 00:05:01,921
Jeong Hoon was originally her tutor.

104
00:05:02,621 --> 00:05:04,090
He changed and...

105
00:05:04,090 --> 00:05:06,830
I feel sorry and angry for Soon Young.

106
00:05:07,501 --> 00:05:09,530
Do you know where I just was?

107
00:05:09,530 --> 00:05:12,730
I went to Daeguk's CEO's home and tore up the living room.

108
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:13,801
What?

109
00:05:14,571 --> 00:05:16,941
Give your brother a message.

110
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:19,671
I won't let him desert Soon Young...

111
00:05:19,671 --> 00:05:22,580
and marry into that family. I just won't.

112
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:26,150
Soon Young doesn't seem to know yet.

113
00:05:26,150 --> 00:05:28,020
We'll never be in-laws.

114
00:05:28,020 --> 00:05:30,150
Your brother ruined that.

115
00:05:30,251 --> 00:05:33,960
I don't think you should tell Soon Young for now.

116
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:37,160
She's still in a state of shock.

117
00:05:37,261 --> 00:05:39,290
This news will just make it worse.

118
00:05:40,501 --> 00:05:41,761
I'm so angry.

119
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,910
Don't just sit and mope.

120
00:05:52,910 --> 00:05:54,011
It's a horrible sight.

121
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,280
You missed work?

122
00:05:56,441 --> 00:05:58,051
Jeong Tae was just...

123
00:05:58,051 --> 00:05:59,480
We met.

124
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,580
He's Jeong Hoon's brother.

125
00:06:01,921 --> 00:06:04,821
I found out just now when he came to find you.

126
00:06:05,821 --> 00:06:08,460
Where did you go instead of to work?

127
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:10,220
I went to see Jeong Hoon...

128
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,890
Did you go to his home again?

129
00:06:11,890 --> 00:06:13,590
No, to Daeguk...

130
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:16,330
It's best you don't know.

131
00:06:17,001 --> 00:06:18,470
What do you mean?

132
00:06:18,470 --> 00:06:20,371
Don't ask. You don't need to know.

133
00:06:25,241 --> 00:06:26,270
Jeong Hoon.

134
00:06:27,111 --> 00:06:29,080
It's not yet over with her?

135
00:06:29,511 --> 00:06:30,650
What do you mean?

136
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:33,451
That woman's aunt caused a scene at my house.

137
00:06:36,150 --> 00:06:39,090
You promised you'd end it and you should have.

138
00:06:39,350 --> 00:06:41,761
How could you let them come to my house?

139
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:45,330
Did you lie to me?

140
00:06:47,131 --> 00:06:49,131
She supported you for years.

141
00:06:49,301 --> 00:06:50,970
How close were you that...

142
00:06:51,201 --> 00:06:53,431
the aunt would say that about you two?

143
00:06:55,171 --> 00:06:56,770
Why won't you say anything?

144
00:06:56,770 --> 00:06:58,210
It's over between us.

145
00:06:58,770 --> 00:07:00,111
What more must I say?

146
00:07:01,311 --> 00:07:04,080
I'm sorry that the aunt trashed your house,

147
00:07:04,350 --> 00:07:07,381
but I find it very unpleasant that you don't believe me.

148
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:10,321
I don't want to marry you...

149
00:07:10,321 --> 00:07:12,691
if I have to keep lying.

150
00:07:13,621 --> 00:07:15,390
You're out of line.

151
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:17,790
You're angry with me?

152
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:19,261
I feel unpleasant.

153
00:07:20,290 --> 00:07:22,400
However much I like you,

154
00:07:22,801 --> 00:07:26,171
if you're so indecisive that you can't end it with a woman,

155
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,741
I'll have to...

156
00:07:29,301 --> 00:07:31,311
reconsider marrying you.

157
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:45,020
What? Jeong Hoon had a fiancee?

158
00:07:45,751 --> 00:07:46,821
Yes.

159
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:49,160
Her aunt was here today...

160
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,491
and caused a scene.

161
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:52,361
Honey.

162
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:56,801
They dated for four years and acted as if they were married.

163
00:07:59,330 --> 00:08:01,270
You didn't know about this, sir?

164
00:08:02,701 --> 00:08:04,171
Why won't you say anything?

165
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,780
Mi Jin knew that he had been seeing someone.

166
00:08:08,410 --> 00:08:10,410
Did you know as well?

167
00:08:10,410 --> 00:08:12,111
He said he'd end it with her.

168
00:08:12,381 --> 00:08:13,881
He promised me.

169
00:08:13,881 --> 00:08:15,051
What?

170
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,150
How could you think of letting him...

171
00:08:17,150 --> 00:08:19,051
marry Mi Jin after that?

172
00:08:19,691 --> 00:08:22,621
Do you know what the woman's aunt said?

173
00:08:23,261 --> 00:08:25,590
She called us thieves!

174
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:27,900
What?

175
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:31,131
We used our money to take another woman's man...

176
00:08:31,131 --> 00:08:32,630
and she called that stealing.

177
00:08:35,970 --> 00:08:37,541
She supported Jeong Hoon...

178
00:08:37,541 --> 00:08:40,311
for four years while he studied for the bar.

179
00:08:40,610 --> 00:08:43,610
Why would he leave her to marry Mi Jin?

180
00:08:44,151 --> 00:08:46,580
It's because of this, our money.

181
00:08:48,021 --> 00:08:49,220
Mi Jin's home.

182
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:51,321
Where were you all day?

183
00:08:51,421 --> 00:08:53,720
- Come and sit down. - I'm tired.

184
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,921
Can I go upstairs, Dad?

185
00:08:57,230 --> 00:08:58,531
Did you meet Jeong Hoon?

186
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,391
Yes.

187
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:03,500
- What did he say? - He ended it with her.

188
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:06,470
The woman's aunt came here to cause a fuss...

189
00:09:06,571 --> 00:09:07,571
and it's over?

190
00:09:08,401 --> 00:09:10,340
Jeong Hoon broke it off and she...

191
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:12,311
came here because she was angry!

192
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:16,311
I will never accept him!

193
00:09:17,010 --> 00:09:19,781
I can't let Mi Jin marry someone who has...

194
00:09:19,781 --> 00:09:21,551
an ulterior motive to marrying her.

195
00:09:25,421 --> 00:09:28,321
Sir, do you think you can trust Jeong Hoon?

196
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:30,220
You keep quiet.

197
00:09:36,031 --> 00:09:37,830
You're back from work?

198
00:09:38,130 --> 00:09:39,301
Is Jeong Hoon in?

199
00:09:39,301 --> 00:09:40,901
Yes. Why?

200
00:09:44,370 --> 00:09:45,671
Jeong Tae's home?

201
00:09:45,671 --> 00:09:47,911
Yes, but he went into Jeong Hoon's room.

202
00:09:48,141 --> 00:09:49,210
Did he?

203
00:09:51,551 --> 00:09:53,411
Are you still getting married?

204
00:09:55,181 --> 00:09:56,181
Yes.

205
00:09:56,421 --> 00:09:58,451
If you want to try to change my mind, get out.

206
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:00,021
Today, Soon Young...

207
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:03,061
You two broke up.

208
00:10:03,061 --> 00:10:04,791
Is it Ms. Uhm now?

209
00:10:05,490 --> 00:10:08,130
Anyway, her aunt went to Daeguk Construction's...

210
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:10,301
CEO's house today.

211
00:10:12,931 --> 00:10:14,641
What did you say?

212
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:18,141
Soon Young's aunt went to Mi Jin's home?

213
00:10:18,441 --> 00:10:20,811
How do you know that?

214
00:10:20,911 --> 00:10:24,051
Soon Young's aunt works where I do.

215
00:10:24,411 --> 00:10:26,681
She missed work so I went to get her and...

216
00:10:26,850 --> 00:10:28,321
found out who she was.

217
00:10:31,090 --> 00:10:33,821
You can guess what happened, can't you?

218
00:10:34,191 --> 00:10:35,561
I'm telling you because she...

219
00:10:35,561 --> 00:10:36,821
told me to, not because I'm worried.

220
00:10:37,661 --> 00:10:39,931
I told you, so I did my part.

221
00:10:46,931 --> 00:10:49,541
They didn't know about Soon Young.

222
00:10:49,801 --> 00:10:51,370
They'll be in shock.

223
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,311
Jeong Hoon.

224
00:10:54,041 --> 00:10:55,681
It's not too late to...

225
00:10:55,681 --> 00:10:57,651
We won't break up because of Soon Young.

226
00:11:10,661 --> 00:11:12,130
(Storage)

227
00:11:15,860 --> 00:11:18,401
The storage room is always dirty.

228
00:11:20,301 --> 00:11:21,301
Bok Shil.

229
00:11:25,071 --> 00:11:27,210
Sorry for letting you down.

230
00:11:28,281 --> 00:11:30,951
But I can't give up on becoming a singer.

231
00:11:35,521 --> 00:11:38,021
I swear there was an egg in here.

232
00:11:38,021 --> 00:11:39,720
Where did it go?

233
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,291
It's not like...

234
00:11:41,291 --> 00:11:43,830
eggs have legs with which to run off on.

235
00:11:44,061 --> 00:11:45,191
My goodness.

236
00:11:46,990 --> 00:11:48,031
Gosh.

237
00:11:48,401 --> 00:11:51,500
What's wrong with your face?

238
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:54,100
- What's that? - Raw egg to make me pretty.

239
00:11:54,470 --> 00:11:56,441
I need to make sure...

240
00:11:56,441 --> 00:11:57,911
I don't get betrayed.

241
00:11:58,141 --> 00:11:59,610
What do you mean?

242
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:03,080
Why do you think Jeong Hoon left his girlfriend for someone else?

243
00:12:03,441 --> 00:12:05,781
Kyung Ho's CEO's daughter is pretty,

244
00:12:05,781 --> 00:12:07,321
that's why.

245
00:12:07,321 --> 00:12:10,120
Do you think it's because she's pretty?

246
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:12,750
He fell in love with her money.

247
00:12:12,990 --> 00:12:15,391
What's wrong with your face, Choon Ja?

248
00:12:15,391 --> 00:12:16,990
You look like a yellow ghost.

249
00:12:17,061 --> 00:12:18,891
- A yellow ghost? - A yellow ghost?

250
00:12:19,330 --> 00:12:21,161
You look scary.

251
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:23,130
Kyung Ho, have breakfast.

252
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,330
I'm not hungry. See you.

253
00:12:25,330 --> 00:12:27,340
Why aren't you hungry?

254
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:28,701
Do you feel unwell?

255
00:12:28,701 --> 00:12:31,041
No. I'll grab something if I feel hungry.

256
00:12:31,041 --> 00:12:32,071
See you.

257
00:12:33,610 --> 00:12:35,441
Is something on his mind?

258
00:12:35,541 --> 00:12:38,250
Why would he leave without breakfast?

259
00:12:39,551 --> 00:12:40,921
Open the door.

260
00:12:41,250 --> 00:12:43,080
Give me that.

261
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,090
The missing egg from the kitchen...

262
00:12:45,451 --> 00:12:47,191
went on your face?

263
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,391
Yes.

264
00:12:49,291 --> 00:12:51,590
Don't make me talk, my skin's too taut.

265
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:52,830
You silly thing.

266
00:12:52,931 --> 00:12:56,330
You're pretty enough that you don't have to do that.

267
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:57,571
Wash your face.

268
00:12:57,571 --> 00:12:59,470
I'll bring in the breakfast table.

269
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,801
You don't even have...

270
00:13:03,041 --> 00:13:06,571
a boy who cares about you.

271
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,641
I do. Jeong Tae...

272
00:13:13,451 --> 00:13:14,521
Jeong Hoon.

273
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:17,691
Are you here to see me?

274
00:13:17,691 --> 00:13:19,821
Yes. My CEO's nephew...

275
00:13:19,821 --> 00:13:21,460
wants to see you.

276
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:22,760
Me?

277
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:26,360
