432
00:20:58,181 --> 00:21:00,451
- Is this it? - Yes.

433
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:01,820
Call her.

434
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:03,181
When we met yesterday,

435
00:21:03,181 --> 00:21:05,391
