443
00:21:29,341 --> 00:21:30,681
Soon Young, are you in?

444
00:21:35,081 --> 00:21:36,220
Soon Young.

445
00:21:37,020 --> 00:21:38,091
Ma'am.

446
00:21:38,651 --> 00:21:40,790
- Hello. - Let's talk.

447
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:45,490
Come in.

448
00:21:45,490 --> 00:21:47,701
- You can go. - Grandma.

449
00:21:53,841 --> 00:21:55,970
