451
00:22:03,951 --> 00:22:05,010
Soon Young.

452
00:22:06,550 --> 00:22:08,081
Yes, Grandma.

453
00:22:09,181 --> 00:22:10,381
I came...

454
00:22:11,151 --> 00:22:14,020
to ask you to do something for me.

455
00:22:16,921 --> 00:22:18,191
Can't you...

456
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:21,431
give up on Jeong Hoon?

457
00:22:23,601 --> 00:22:24,970
Grandma.

458
00:22:24,970 --> 00:22:26,401
At first,

459
00:22:27,270 --> 00:22:29,500
