469
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,240
completely changed his mind.

470
00:23:06,841 --> 00:23:10,441
Ok Boon is very distraught over all this,

471
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:13,280
and what's worse,

472
00:23:14,220 --> 00:23:17,851
it's causing a rift between the kids and I can't stand that.

473
00:23:19,651 --> 00:23:20,720
So...

474
00:23:21,091 --> 00:23:24,661
I came to ask you for a favor.

475
00:23:25,060 --> 00:23:26,560
For Jeong Hoon's sake,

476
00:23:27,701 --> 00:23:29,861
can you not let him go?

477
00:23:36,101 --> 00:23:37,841
I'm so sorry that...

478
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:39,770
this is...

479
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:43,280
all I can say to you.

480
00:23:47,351 --> 00:23:48,951
As you know,

481
00:23:50,121 --> 00:23:53,750
I owe Jeong Hoon a lot.

482
00:23:55,490 --> 00:23:57,161
That's why now...

483
00:23:58,161 --> 00:24:00,260
