555
00:27:25,871 --> 00:27:26,970
Kyung Ho.

556
00:27:27,371 --> 00:27:29,841
I didn't tell you I joined Lucky Entertainment...

557
00:27:29,841 --> 00:27:31,441
I'll go first, Bok Shil.

558
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,941
You lied to me.

559
00:27:36,141 --> 00:27:37,151
Okay.

560
00:27:37,411 --> 00:27:39,611
I don't want you to sing,

561
00:27:39,611 --> 00:27:41,921
so you couldn't tell me. I get that.

562
00:27:43,951 --> 00:27:45,720
But now that I know,

563
00:27:46,490 --> 00:27:48,691
I don't want you to go on working there.

564
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:50,960
- Leave. - Kyung Ho.

565
00:27:51,131 --> 00:27:53,091
The CEO makes you clean.

566
00:27:53,831 --> 00:27:55,000
You went to sing.

567
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:56,361
Does that make sense?

568
00:27:58,101 --> 00:27:59,201
So quit.

569
00:27:59,770 --> 00:28:02,371
I'll contact the company that offered the clerk job.

570
00:28:03,040 --> 00:28:04,111
No.

571
00:28:04,371 --> 00:28:06,371
I'll become a singer and succeed.

572
00:28:06,371 --> 00:28:07,480
Bok Shil.

573
00:28:07,710 --> 00:28:10,480
If you're going to object to my being a singer,

574
00:28:12,210 --> 00:28:13,980
then stop minding my business.

575
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:19,091
You asked to see me, so I thought about it.

576
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:22,891
I can't give up on my dream.

577
00:28:23,290 --> 00:28:24,391
You give up.

578
00:28:24,831 --> 00:28:26,530
Stop liking me.

579
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:30,000
How can you say that so easily?

580
00:28:30,331 --> 00:28:31,671
It wasn't easy.

581
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:34,671
I thought and agonized over it.

582
00:28:35,570 --> 00:28:39,540
I haven't worked at Lucky Entertainment for too long.

583
00:28:39,540 --> 00:28:41,941
Even if you see me, pretend we're strangers.

584
00:28:42,310 --> 00:28:44,710
I'll feel uncomfortable if the CEO were to know.

585
00:28:45,411 --> 00:28:46,611
I have to go.

586
00:28:48,351 --> 00:28:49,351
Bok Shil.

587
00:28:55,691 --> 00:28:58,161
What? Jeong Hoon's grandma was here?

588
00:28:59,931 --> 00:29:02,060
And? What did she say?

589
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,230
She asked me to...

590
00:29:04,970 --> 00:29:06,431
let Jeong Hoon go.

591
00:29:06,601 --> 00:29:07,701
What?

592
00:29:07,871 --> 00:29:10,841
Now the old woman's trying to get rid of you too?

593
00:29:11,441 --> 00:29:13,881
She asked me to do her a favor.

594
00:29:14,911 --> 00:29:17,510
Jeong Hoon's mother is very upset,

595
00:29:17,681 --> 00:29:21,081
and she can't stand watching Jeong Hoon argue with his siblings.

596
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:24,921
She held my hand and pleaded.

597
00:29:26,220 --> 00:29:28,591
It's all about the money.

598
00:29:29,790 --> 00:29:32,530
What did you say? Did you just sit and cry?

599
00:29:32,891 --> 00:29:34,560
There was nothing...

600
00:29:35,460 --> 00:29:36,901
I could say after that.

601
00:29:37,431 --> 00:29:39,030
You should've spoken your mind.

602
00:29:39,030 --> 00:29:40,641
Why didn't you?

603
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:49,181
What? You met Soon Young?

604
00:29:49,881 --> 00:29:50,951
Yes.

605
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:54,480
I asked her to give up on Jeong Hoon,

606
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,780
so that's that.

607
00:29:55,780 --> 00:29:57,891
How could you go all the way there...

608
00:29:57,990 --> 00:30:00,020
and ask her to do that?

609
00:30:00,391 --> 00:30:02,060
Should we just sit and watch, then?

610
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:05,591
Do you think Jeong Hoon will change his mind?

611
00:30:05,591 --> 00:30:07,431
Don't you know your own son?

612
00:30:07,431 --> 00:30:09,701
Why wouldn't I know my son?

613
00:30:10,201 --> 00:30:13,030
He didn't leave Soon Young because he fell out of love...

614
00:30:13,570 --> 00:30:16,841
and he isn't marrying Mi Jin because he loves her.

615
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:22,111
He's lashing out because he thinks his father...

616
00:30:22,111 --> 00:30:24,010
ruined his life.

617
00:30:24,010 --> 00:30:25,651
That's why we must stop him.

618
00:30:25,951 --> 00:30:28,280
He didn't make these decisions with a clear mind.

619
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:29,921
We must stop him.

620
00:30:29,921 --> 00:30:31,921
Yes, like you said,

621
00:30:31,921 --> 00:30:34,421
because of his dad, his acceptance to...

622
00:30:35,161 --> 00:30:37,290
the judicial institute was cancelled...

623
00:30:37,290 --> 00:30:38,960
and he can't work anywhere.

624
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,331
Should he just give up like that?

625
00:30:44,601 --> 00:30:47,270
He'll have to work as a manual laborer.

626
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:50,000
Can you deal with that?

627
00:30:50,641 --> 00:30:53,070
If they will offer him a good career,

628
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:55,510
we must grab hold of whoever we can.

629
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:56,980
That way,

630
00:30:56,980 --> 00:30:59,250
Jeong Hoon will get a life of his own.

631
00:30:59,681 --> 00:31:02,121
Don't you try to stop me.

632
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:08,861
Did you talk to Jeong Hoon?

633
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:11,631
Yes, he came to my office.

634
00:31:11,631 --> 00:31:12,691
What did he say?

635
00:31:13,901 --> 00:31:15,901
He said he'd end it properly,

636
00:31:15,901 --> 00:31:17,631
so I gave him another chance.

637
00:31:18,401 --> 00:31:20,431
Why won't he call me then?

638
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:24,810
I told him that I'd have to think about marrying him.

639
00:31:25,341 --> 00:31:27,581
You said that?

640
00:31:27,581 --> 00:31:29,010
He said it was over,

641
00:31:29,010 --> 00:31:31,510
but the woman's aunt caused a fuss and I got angry.

642
00:31:32,081 --> 00:31:33,881
What do you really want?

643
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:37,351
Did you really decide to reconsider marriage?

644
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:40,560
No, Dad. I blurted that out in anger.

645
00:31:41,820 --> 00:31:43,861
If he were to come and ask for forgiveness,

646
00:31:43,861 --> 00:31:45,260
I'd forgive him for everything.

647
00:31:45,260 --> 00:31:46,790
Why hasn't he called?

648
00:31:48,530 --> 00:31:50,770
He's not that easy to manipulate.

649
00:31:51,171 --> 00:31:53,300
He knows you were angry...

650
00:31:53,631 --> 00:31:55,641
and is waiting for you to calm down.

651
00:31:55,770 --> 00:31:57,841
That's why I feel worse.

652
00:31:57,841 --> 00:32:00,681
It's like I always give in to him.

653
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:17,990
Why won't my heart slow down even after I take a pill?

654
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:20,131
You, come here.

655
00:32:21,601 --> 00:32:22,631
What for?

656
00:32:24,131 --> 00:32:26,931
You can't marry him.

657
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:29,300
I'll do whatever it takes...

658
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:30,810
to break you two up.

659
00:32:30,810 --> 00:32:32,310
Will you stop it?

660
00:32:32,671 --> 00:32:34,510
I'm upset too.

661
00:32:34,581 --> 00:32:37,381
Why should you get upset over him?

662
00:32:37,381 --> 00:32:39,210
When you can just give up?

663
00:32:39,381 --> 00:32:42,320
It's my marriage. I'll deal with it!

664
00:32:43,381 --> 00:32:44,490
Mi Jin!

665
00:32:49,020 --> 00:32:52,391
Sang Pil, what is she talking about?

666
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:54,631
What will she deal with?

667
00:32:54,861 --> 00:32:57,131
She's not over him yet, is he?

668
00:32:58,131 --> 00:33:00,871
I think you should talk to her.

669
00:33:01,401 --> 00:33:04,111
Jeong Hoon wants to marry Mi Jin for a reason...

670
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:05,810
and that bothers me.

671
00:33:05,810 --> 00:33:08,540
Right? You think so too?

672
00:33:09,540 --> 00:33:12,581
I will cancel this engagement.

673
00:33:19,351 --> 00:33:20,720
What's this stink?

674
00:33:24,391 --> 00:33:25,760
This is the house.

675
00:33:28,401 --> 00:33:30,931
- Wait here. - Yes, ma'am.

676
00:33:35,871 --> 00:33:39,141
Who are you?

677
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:42,081
Does Oh Jeong Hoon live here?

678
00:33:42,810 --> 00:33:44,310
Yes, he does.

679
00:33:45,250 --> 00:33:47,220
Are you his mother?

680
00:33:48,851 --> 00:33:49,951
Yes.

681
00:33:51,921 --> 00:33:53,520
I'm Mi Jin's mother.

682
00:33:54,220 --> 00:33:55,260
What?

683
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:57,691
This is unbelievable.

684
00:33:58,861 --> 00:34:01,861
Do you know why I came all the way here?

685
00:34:04,701 --> 00:34:08,040
I'm here to call off the engagement between our kids.

686
00:34:29,161 --> 00:34:32,931
(Through the Waves)

687
00:34:33,390 --> 00:34:35,631
Do you know how shameless you both are?

688
00:34:35,631 --> 00:34:37,530
You should be more aggressive.

689
00:34:37,530 --> 00:34:39,401
Just because your son is smart,

690
00:34:39,401 --> 00:34:40,541
you sell him over.

691
00:34:40,541 --> 00:34:41,771
How can you say that?

692
00:34:41,771 --> 00:34:43,240
- Let's go and eat. - What?

693
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:44,611
What should we do now?

694
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:47,081
You won't understand or accept me.

695
00:34:47,081 --> 00:34:48,680
That's what's happening.

696
00:34:48,680 --> 00:34:49,941
I like you as...

697
00:34:49,941 --> 00:34:51,711
you are now, not as a singer.

698
00:34:52,450 --> 00:34:53,851
What'll you do about Soon Young?

699
00:34:53,851 --> 00:34:55,421
Doing this won't change anything.

700
00:34:55,421 --> 00:34:56,921
I won't do that kind of job.

701
00:34:56,921 --> 00:34:58,820
Just make sure that nothing goes wrong.

702
00:34:58,820 --> 00:34:59,851
Get out the way!

